an id='c66f3150704d4148819136c75488d7e5_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1038&endYear=1038')\">1038年</a>，17岁</div><div id='c66f3150704d4148819136c75488d7e5' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1038&endYear=1038')\">1038年</a>，读书于潜山。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"352f4fe6b3f4481587be25fd1deb2225\");'><span id='352f4fe6b3f4481587be25fd1deb2225_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1039&endYear=1039')\">1039年</a>，18岁</div><div id='352f4fe6b3f4481587be25fd1deb2225' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1039&endYear=1039')\">1039年</a>，读书于潜山，父冯式卒；再继室后富氏夫人出生。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《偷狗赋》<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.454549,"Longitude":116.051546,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN360427","Title":"星子","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8820879d6df14ede85ca8a27981d8498\");'><span id='8820879d6df14ede85ca8a27981d8498_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1036&endYear=1037')\">1036-1037年</a>，15-16岁</div><div id='8820879d6df14ede85ca8a27981d8498' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1036&endYear=1036')\">1036年</a>，短期随父游学南康，读书于幽邃庵。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1037&endYear=1037')\">1037年</a>，游学南康，<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.319213,"Longitude":115.762628,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN360426","Title":"德安","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"d0c181be2b8943c6bcb77730d71515e9\");'><span id='d0c181be2b8943c6bcb77730d71515e9_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1037&endYear=1037')\">1037年</a>，16岁</div><div id='d0c181be2b8943c6bcb77730d71515e9' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1037&endYear=1037')\">1037年</a>，访德安王氏义学，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>题三万王氏义学。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.548594,"Longitude":117.070127,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3408","Title":"安庆","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f26197dcf9b14850a13e8bae5702b087\");'><span id='f26197dcf9b14850a13e8bae5702b087_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1038&endYear=1038')\">1038年</a>，17岁</div><div id='f26197dcf9b14850a13e8bae5702b087' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1038&endYear=1038')\">1038年</a>，游学安庆，读书于万松山。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.559627,"Longitude":114.322539,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN420106","Title":"武昌","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f12871dc7e7c40d6b9f4df5a667610c4\");'><span id='f12871dc7e7c40d6b9f4df5a667610c4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1040&endYear=1044')\">1040-1044年</a>，19-23岁</div><div id='f12871dc7e7c40d6b9f4df5a667610c4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1040&endYear=1040')\">1040年</a>，母朱氏携诸孤居鄂州，自教读书，以教子为乐。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1041&endYear=1043')\">1041-1043年</a>，寓武昌。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1044&endYear=1044')\">1044年</a>，寓武昌，困顿仕途，纵饮不羁。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7d4cc8ebcf4d4d3eb05355e5d9011fca\");'><span id='7d4cc8ebcf4d4d3eb05355e5d9011fca_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1046&endYear=1048')\">1046-1048年</a>，25-27岁</div><div id='7d4cc8ebcf4d4d3eb05355e5d9011fca' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1046&endYear=1046')\">1046年</a>，寓武昌，母朱氏广交贤达，为营造环境。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1047&endYear=1047')\">1047年</a>，寓武昌。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1048&endYear=1048')\">1048年8月</a>，参加鄂州乡试，得鄂倅南宫诚力荐，中举人第一名——解元。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"bffa65c13cbc4f9e9f05f9993e942715\");'><span id='bffa65c13cbc4f9e9f05f9993e942715_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，28岁</div><div id='bffa65c13cbc4f9e9f05f9993e942715' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，还鄂，才子得意，题诗江亭。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.42439,"Longitude":120.305092,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN330110","Title":"余杭","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"03027268940347b3bcd304a6123536cf\");'><span id='03027268940347b3bcd304a6123536cf_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1045&endYear=1045')\">1045年</a>，24岁</div><div id='03027268940347b3bcd304a6123536cf' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1045&endYear=1045')\">1045年</a>，客余杭县，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《题寺壁》<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">题寺壁（宋·冯京）<br />　　七言绝句　押东韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->韩信栖迟项羽穷，手提长剑喝秋风。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->吁嗟天下苍生眼，不识男儿未济中<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 宋方勺《泊宅编》卷上　《泊宅编》：冯当世未第时，客馀杭县，为官逋拘窘，计无所出，题小诗于所寓寺壁云云，胥为白令，即获释。</span></div></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"583a80799bb047ccad5e80dc313cb1ac\");'><span id='583a80799bb047ccad5e80dc313cb1ac_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，28岁</div><div id='583a80799bb047ccad5e80dc313cb1ac' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年3月13日</a>，礼部奏名进士第一。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年3月21日</a>，殿试第一，有谢启。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《谢状元及第启》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，张尧佐逼婚，以“老母尝议王氏”拒之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，归即纳采娶王氏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，与同榜第三人钱公辅定交。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年4月7日</a>，将作监丞、通判荆南府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年4月26日</a>，仁宗赐御诗及《中庸》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，将归鄂州，司马光有诗相送。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"0f01c6e6c2924418b20883e73da2c02d\");'><span id='0f01c6e6c2924418b20883e73da2c02d_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1052&endYear=1058')\">1052-1058年</a>，31-37岁</div><div id='0f01c6e6c2924418b20883e73da2c02d' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1052&endYear=1052')\">1052年</a>，迁秘书省秘书郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1053&endYear=1053')\">1053年8月7日</a>，召试，迁太常丞、直集贤院。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1054&endYear=1054')\">1054年</a>，太常丞、直集贤院同判吏部南曹。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1054&endYear=1054')\">1054年</a>，续娶富氏夫人，是为前富氏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1054&endYear=1054')\">1054年8月2日</a>，同判登闻鼓院。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1054&endYear=1054')\">1054年11月6日</a>，因言吴充、鞠真卿不当补外，落同修起居注。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1054&endYear=1054')\">1054年11月27日</a>，知制诰刘敞连上两奏，为辩不公。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1055&endYear=1055')\">1055年</a>，长子冯谌生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1055&endYear=1055')\">1055年3月13日</a>，前富氏卒于京师。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1055&endYear=1055')\">1055年5月</a>，复为太常丞、直集贤院、同修起居注。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1056&endYear=1057')\">1056-1057年</a>，在太常丞、直集贤院、同修起居注任上。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1058&endYear=1058')\">1058年</a>，再续娶后富氏夫人。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"ae0525f9ccf548d2888c0ace22e45c11\");'><span id='ae0525f9ccf548d2888c0ace22e45c11_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1061&endYear=1065')\">1061-1065年</a>，40-44岁</div><div id='ae0525f9ccf548d2888c0ace22e45c11' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1061&endYear=1061')\">1061年4月9日</a>，迁翰林侍读学士。召还，纠察在京刑狱。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1062&endYear=1062')\">1062年</a>，任翰林侍读学士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1062&endYear=1062')\">1062年10月</a>，迁翰林学士、知制诰，权知开封府事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1063&endYear=1063')\">1063年</a>，为翰林学士、知制诰，权知开封府事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1063&endYear=1063')\">1063年4月4日</a>，仁宗崩，冯京为桥道顿递使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1063&endYear=1063')\">1063年4月</a>，英宗即位，转官加勋。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1063&endYear=1063')\">1063年11月</a>，与王圭等谦让张方平先朝见。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1064&endYear=1064')\">1064年</a>，数月不诣丞相府，韩琦以为京傲。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1064&endYear=1064')\">1064年6月</a>，上奏请避岳父宰相富弼嫌，请解开封府事补外。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1064&endYear=1064')\">1064年</a>，列章自咎，待罪特放。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年1月9日</a>，权知贡举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年3月9日</a>，引新赐及第进士彭汝砺已下诣垂拱殿见谢恩。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年3月</a>，母朱氏夫人病，数请归，上抚之甚厚。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b6b5d62e66b54f24a56e54871b85c5ab\");'><span id='b6b5d62e66b54f24a56e54871b85c5ab_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年</a>，44岁</div><div id='b6b5d62e66b54f24a56e54871b85c5ab' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年10月</a>，为南郊礼仪使。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f216c8c1b513460b95ef981f94de36ca\");'><span id='f216c8c1b513460b95ef981f94de36ca_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1068')\">1065-1068年</a>，44-47岁</div><div id='f216c8c1b513460b95ef981f94de36ca' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年12月</a>，任馆伴契丹使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1066&endYear=1066')\">1066年1月26日</a>，修撰仁宗实录。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1066&endYear=1066')\">1066年4月</a>，乞下礼院议祝文体式。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1066&endYear=1066')\">1066年8月24日</a>，母朱氏卒，享年七十二。友人刘攽有挽诗。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1066&endYear=1068')\">1066-1068年</a>，居家丁母忧。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年11月</a>，服除，复为学士。迁尚书礼部郎中、知制诰。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"bb88e87a4e5b4618aea0df6f65bff672\");'><span id='bb88e87a4e5b4618aea0df6f65bff672_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1074')\">1070-1074年</a>，49-53岁</div><div id='bb88e87a4e5b4618aea0df6f65bff672' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年4月8日</a>，任翰林学士兼端明殿学士、知开封府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年4月17日</a>，以翰林学士兼端明殿学士、礼部郎中、知制诰权御史中丞。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年6月</a>，任河东安抚使，有奏文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《乞官为借支三州义军衣甲以应敌奏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年6月18日</a>，诏冯京同三司都理欠司相度合放系欠官物。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年6月19日</a>，上奏朱温其权发遣大理少卿不当。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《朱温其权发遣大理少卿不当奏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年6月22日</a>，上疏言薛向除天章阁待制不当。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《薛向除待制不当奏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年7月4日</a>，为右谏议大夫、枢密副使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年7月7日</a>，举荐孙奕任御史未果。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年9月</a>，以河东麟、府等州城垒兵械不治自劾，诏释其罪。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《以河东麟府等州城垒兵械不治自劾奏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年9月14日</a>，进参知政事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年</a>，荐刘攽、苏轼掌外制。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1071')\">1071年6月1日</a>，明堂大礼，为仪仗使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1071')\">1071年6月11日</a>，欧阳修上章乞骸骨，以太子少师、观文殿学士致仕，冯京请留之不果。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1072&endYear=1072')\">1072年2月4日</a>，与神宗论保甲法利弊。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1072&endYear=1072')\">1072年闰79日</a>，为如京副使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1073&endYear=1073')\">1073年2月27日</a>，与王安石辩不当用沈起。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1073&endYear=1073')\">1073年11月</a>，举荐王安国为著作佐郎秘阁校理。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年</a>，久旱不雨，请刘攽代作待罪表。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年4月8日</a>，与神宗论市易事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年4月19日</a>，王安石罢相，乃与韩绛、吕惠卿同僚。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年5月14日</a>，吕惠卿罢制举，冯京反对无果。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年</a>，乞退不允。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"6782ab47f683419796a27a1191c83b0a\");'><span id='6782ab47f683419796a27a1191c83b0a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1080')\">1076-1080年</a>，55-59岁</div><div id='6782ab47f683419796a27a1191c83b0a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年11月4日</a>，兼群牧制置使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年1月</a>，知成都府任上乞修永康军城及举荐俞充、段介等请示得答复。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年5月9日</a>，诏修仁宗、英宗史，赐筵史院，有诗与同僚唱和。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《诏修两朝国史赐筵史院和首相吴公原韵》<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">诏修两朝国史赐筵史院和首相吴公原韵（宋·冯京）<br />　　五言律诗　押鱼韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->天密丛云晓，风清一雨馀。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->三长太史笔，二典帝皇<span class=\"small\">①</span>书。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->按武知何者，沾恩匪幸欤。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->吐茵平日事，何惮污公车<span class=\"small\">②</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 《宋诗纪事》卷一八引作王　② 宋王明清《挥麈后录》卷一</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年10月</a>，友人程师孟知越州，有诗相送。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《送程给事知越州》<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">送程给事知越州（宋·冯京）<br />　　七言律诗　押真韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->才毫无地展经纶，白首归来万里身。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->持节气凌沙漠使，怀章荣动会稽人。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->平湖翠岫千家月，落日西风一箸莼。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->南海疲民正回首，满城歌舞颂年椿<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 宋黄康弼《续会稽掇英集》卷一</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年11月8日</a>，进言辩白谢景初无罪。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年</a>，疾病，神宗使医为治。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年8月</a>，疾愈造朝。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年11月5日</a>，与吴充、王圭等请罢赐功臣号，从之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1079')\">1079年</a>，在枢密使任上。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年1月11日</a>，诣启圣禅院，行朝拜礼。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年5月2日</a>，司天监定九月明堂大礼，冯京为礼仪使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年9月27日</a>，明堂大礼，冯京迁正议大夫、枢密使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年9月28日</a>，吕公著为枢密副使，于是西府同僚有吕公著、薛向、孙固等。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年</a>，受成都府嘉祐禅院纪师之托，作《嘉祐禅院记》<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"5021656e84ca4fad9f61eacac7f26d7c\");'><span id='5021656e84ca4fad9f61eacac7f26d7c_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年</a>，66岁</div><div id='5021656e84ca4fad9f61eacac7f26d7c' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年7月16日</a>，坤成节，进奉马匹，有赐诏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年12月7日</a>，进奉兴龙节马并冬节马，有赐诏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年12月26日</a>，进奉贺端午节马。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"5d9d17a92c674c0c853de431dd2ccf81\");'><span id='5d9d17a92c674c0c853de431dd2ccf81_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1094')\">1091-1094年</a>，70-73岁</div><div id='5d9d17a92c674c0c853de431dd2ccf81' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1091')\">1091年1月11日</a>，有徙知陈州之命，过国门，辞疾甚。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1091')\">1091年1月12日</a>，改左银青光禄大夫、观文殿学士、兼侍读，充中太一宫使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1091')\">1091年2月1日</a>，初赴侍读。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1091')\">1091年4月12日</a>，乞致仕不允，令除经筵外，遇朔望赴朝参。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1091')\">1091年5月22日</a>，除宣徽南院使，仍旧充中太一宫使，许朝朔望。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1091')\">1091年闰8</a>，再上表乞致仕，不许、不允。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1092&endYear=1092')\">1092年3月4日</a>，为太子少师、依旧宣徽南院使致仕。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1092&endYear=1092')\">1092年8月26日</a>，宣徽南院使致仕冯京为太子少傅。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1093&endYear=1093')\">1093年</a>，致仕休养。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1094&endYear=1094')\">1094年4月3日</a>，卒。讣闻，天子为特行临奠之礼，赠司徒，谥曰文简。蔡骃为撰行状，彭汝砺为撰墓志。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.340606,"Longitude":112.24722,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN421","Title":"荆州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"dbbe45a831b14fbe9c56e8b20cbaf7a9\");'><span id='dbbe45a831b14fbe9c56e8b20cbaf7a9_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1051')\">1049-1051年</a>，28-30岁</div><div id='dbbe45a831b14fbe9c56e8b20cbaf7a9' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1049&endYear=1049')\">1049年</a>，恩人南宫诚通判长沙，有诗谢知遇之恩。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《谢鄂倅南宫诚》<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">谢鄂倅南宫城（宋·冯京）<br />　　七言律诗　押寒韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->尝思鹏海隔飞翻，曾得<span class=\"small\">①</span>天风送羽翰。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->恩比丘山何以戴，心同金石欲移难。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->经年空叹音书绝，千里常思道义欢。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->每向江陵访遗治<span class=\"small\">②</span>，邑人犹指县题看<span class=\"small\">③</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 《宋历科状元录》卷三作是<br />② 《宋历科状元录》作迹<br />③ 宋文莹《湘山野录》卷中　《湘山野录》：冯大参当世，始求荐于武昌。会小宗者庸缪寡鉴，坚欲黜落，又欲置末缀。时鄂倅南宫城监试，当拆封定卷，大不平，奋臂力主之，以公冠于乡版，果取大魁。释褐除荆南倅，南宫迁潭倅，以诗谢之云云。</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1050&endYear=1050')\">1050年11月19日</a>，原配王氏文淑卒，年二十，子祖善未月亦夭。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1051&endYear=1051')\">1051年</a>，与同僚善处。离任，“吏民拥马首，不听行”<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1051&endYear=1051')\">1051年</a>，嫂朱氏病卒于鄂州太平坊里第。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.39986,"Longitude":119.419107,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN321","Title":"扬州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8d1c68b96ed64dccb6a5728b59339023\");'><span id='8d1c68b96ed64dccb6a5728b59339023_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1058&endYear=1058')\">1058年</a>，37岁</div><div id='8d1c68b96ed64dccb6a5728b59339023' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1058&endYear=1058')\">1058年3月</a>，避岳父富弼亲嫌，迁为右正言、龙图阁待制，知扬州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1058&endYear=1058')\">1058年</a>，在扬州，遇事立断，吏畏民悦。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.82687,"Longitude":117.235447,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3401","Title":"合肥","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"dd9df66671a34edd886d08dbd6960f86\");'><span id='dd9df66671a34edd886d08dbd6960f86_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1059&endYear=1059')\">1059年</a>，38岁</div><div id='dd9df66671a34edd886d08dbd6960f86' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1059&endYear=1059')\">1059年3月18日</a>，因刘保衡案，自劾徙知庐州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1059&endYear=1059')\">1059年</a>，安于治郡，甚得利民心。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"efd2fd4089104bfaaafe23e7f32553ce\");'><span id='efd2fd4089104bfaaafe23e7f32553ce_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1060&endYear=1060')\">1060年</a>，39岁</div><div id='efd2fd4089104bfaaafe23e7f32553ce' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1060&endYear=1060')\">1060年6月</a>，以龙图阁待制知江宁府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1060&endYear=1060')\">1060年</a>，在江宁任上，遇事“据案推究”，“一无壅滞，人服其敏。”<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.347436,"Longitude":108.946306,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN6101","Title":"西安","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8147fd9ebf794b3f884c88b90813f663\");'><span id='8147fd9ebf794b3f884c88b90813f663_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年</a>，44岁</div><div id='8147fd9ebf794b3f884c88b90813f663' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年5月4日</a>，为陕西安抚使。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f39466cad52049129973f4ba0ed8e01a\");'><span id='f39466cad52049129973f4ba0ed8e01a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年</a>，44岁</div><div id='f39466cad52049129973f4ba0ed8e01a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年12月</a>，在陕西安抚使任上，荐种氏。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":37.876885,"Longitude":112.55706,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN1401","Title":"太原","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"adeccae78c954bf8b53e5871268056eb\");'><span id='adeccae78c954bf8b53e5871268056eb_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，48岁</div><div id='adeccae78c954bf8b53e5871268056eb' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，以端明殿学士兼翰林侍读学士，知太原府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，建筹边楼、爱月亭。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，与王安国书信往来谈佛事。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":33.850774,"Longitude":115.785767,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3416","Title":"亳州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"c43813d7d7ec4638b1a0979f73790d63\");'><span id='c43813d7d7ec4638b1a0979f73790d63_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年</a>，54岁</div><div id='c43813d7d7ec4638b1a0979f73790d63' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年1月7日</a>，以参知政事、右谏议大夫守本官罢知亳州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.624376,"Longitude":112.460033,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4103","Title":"洛阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"82c75bdede9649fe8a59cd3795032c32\");'><span id='82c75bdede9649fe8a59cd3795032c32_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年</a>，54岁</div><div id='82c75bdede9649fe8a59cd3795032c32' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年10月29日</a>，知河南府。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8ef3266aa3b54f4b9e45085215735a96\");'><span id='8ef3266aa3b54f4b9e45085215735a96_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年</a>，62岁</div><div id='8ef3266aa3b54f4b9e45085215735a96' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年闰622日</a>，岳父富弼薨于洛阳私第。赴洛阳奔丧。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":35.549266,"Longitude":106.671741,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN6208","Title":"平凉","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"6036ae2a170a4d7f9cdeb2ed55c60a96\");'><span id='6036ae2a170a4d7f9cdeb2ed55c60a96_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1076')\">1075-1076年</a>，54-55岁</div><div id='6036ae2a170a4d7f9cdeb2ed55c60a96' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年11月9日</a>，为资政殿学士、知渭州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年2月</a>，知渭州，兼泾原路经略使。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.576279,"Longitude":104.071216,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN5101","Title":"成都","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"55a79a4112414bfcb1704ad90d622d83\");'><span id='55a79a4112414bfcb1704ad90d622d83_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年</a>，55岁</div><div id='55a79a4112414bfcb1704ad90d622d83' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年4月23日</a>，茂州夷人叛，徙知成都府，兼利州路安抚使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年5月12日</a>，修筑边防。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年</a>，收服夷人叛乱，深得人心，苏轼以词盛赞。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年</a>，茂州守将、成都路提点刑狱张讽病还成都，冯京迎候，张讽托之后事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年9月</a>，作《油筒子传》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年10月23日</a>，以给事中召知枢密院。诏京抚定蕃部讫，乃赴阙。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年11月</a>，离成都，蜀人不忍其去，为张灯如上元。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.91365,"Longitude":112.797734,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN410883","Title":"孟州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"612044548a514a668d5bc5b82a300fc5\");'><span id='612044548a514a668d5bc5b82a300fc5_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，60岁</div><div id='612044548a514a668d5bc5b82a300fc5' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年1月23日</a>，罢枢密使，以光禄大夫、观文殿大学士、知河阳。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《河阳谢上表》<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"1bbc5bb924264852a0f17ecafd7cdea6\");'><span id='1bbc5bb924264852a0f17ecafd7cdea6_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1086')\">1084-1086年</a>，63-65岁</div><div id='1bbc5bb924264852a0f17ecafd7cdea6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1084')\">1084年</a>，冬，赴任河阳。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年3月27日</a>，哲宗赐冯京等金带银帛。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年</a>，迁银青光禄大夫。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1086&endYear=1086')\">1086年9月11日</a>，在知河阳任上。文彦博荐其为相，御史中丞刘挚言冯京疾病，事多健忘，不宜为相。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":36.778223,"Longitude":118.440962,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN370781002","Title":"益都","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"27f26201314d4b4598f4382e8d2c0fc6\");'><span id='27f26201314d4b4598f4382e8d2c0fc6_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，60岁</div><div id='27f26201314d4b4598f4382e8d2c0fc6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年11月2日</a>，徙知青州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":38.152193,"Longitude":114.577442,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN130123","Title":"正定","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"c632a3ca721e413398d9b924443f5ae7\");'><span id='c632a3ca721e413398d9b924443f5ae7_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1083')\">1082-1083年</a>，61-62岁</div><div id='c632a3ca721e413398d9b924443f5ae7' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1082')\">1082年</a>，改知真定府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年</a>，在知成德军任上，治理滹沱河。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f52026169fcf4e04b224a810120e0c18\");'><span id='f52026169fcf4e04b224a810120e0c18_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1084')\">1084年</a>，63岁</div><div id='f52026169fcf4e04b224a810120e0c18' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1084')\">1084年7月18日</a>，有复知河阳之命。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1084')\">1084年8月3日</a>，仍在真定府，言洺州水灾事。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":36.291268,"Longitude":115.154493,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN130425","Title":"大名","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"74f5feb9abb341ab9592400a1279b2df\");'><span id='74f5feb9abb341ab9592400a1279b2df_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年</a>，66岁</div><div id='74f5feb9abb341ab9592400a1279b2df' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年3月19日</a>，除保宁军节度使、知大名府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1087&endYear=1087')\">1087年3月</a>，哲宗两敕茶药。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"edb4ce70d6e745b6a9c449a6edd47046\");'><span id='edb4ce70d6e745b6a9c449a6edd47046_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1090')\">1088-1090年</a>，67-69岁</div><div id='edb4ce70d6e745b6a9c449a6edd47046' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年2月12日</a>，乞令有司固护府城横堤。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《乞令有司固护府城横堤奏》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年4月13日</a>，夫人后富氏卒，享年五十。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1088&endYear=1088')\">1088年4月13日</a>，得到皇上多次抚问。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1089&endYear=1089')\">1089年7月12日</a>，右谏议大夫范祖禹荐其可任枢密。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年</a>，春，上表乞致仕，不允、不许。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年</a>，再上表乞致仕，不允、不许。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年</a>，三上表乞致仕，不允、不许，断来章。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年4月26日</a>，为检校司空，改授彰德军节度使，再任知大名府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年4月26日</a>，上表辞免加恩，不允、不许。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年5月</a>，上表辞免彰德军节钺，不允、不许。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年</a>，冬，进奉贺明堂礼。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1090&endYear=1090')\">1090年12月1日</a>，有知河阳之命，未赴任。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.545813,"Longitude":113.396832,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN410183","Title":"新密","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"c4cfd77a35c5427697a68f9ac0f5b716\");'><span id='c4cfd77a35c5427697a68f9ac0f5b716_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1094&endYear=1094')\">1094年</a>，73岁</div><div id='c4cfd77a35c5427697a68f9ac0f5b716' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1094&endYear=1094')\">1094年8月</a>，葬密县义台乡南朱村之祖茔。<br /></div>"}],"Title":"冯京 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1021-1094)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：王可喜《北宋状元冯京年谱》　录入整理：王可喜</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 4, 115.1902565, 29.583168, 10)\">0-17岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">咸宁</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">星子</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">德安</a> → <a h